Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.94,0:00:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things that are, and things that cannot be,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,call out,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and blend together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They become a Mononoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To cut,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to stab,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to gouge,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to carve,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the duties of the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must learn the Mononoke’s name,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,its shape,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,its Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must learn its state of being, its Truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the state of its mind, its Regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, my blade will cleanse it of its fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Mononoke who wishes its Truth to be known.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who committed suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was it that lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean on that stanchion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t you all see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that why you were so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that’s what you meant when\Nyou said there was someone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was standing there, holding the stanchion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared when it started moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh—She was dressed like a fashion model!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was there, holding a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichikawa Setsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.44,0:03:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh—What do you mean? Ichikawa didn’t have a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me? Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t you see it, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the scales,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can only he…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Setsuko-san’s thoughts brought forth the Ghost Cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, at least, is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“I won’t forgive you.”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:04:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone else hear the woman’s voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s the one who killed herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to suffer the consequences?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I{\alpha&HFF&} see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.94,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayor’s death, Ghost Cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone hid something about Ichikawa Setsuko’s death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh—What do you want now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you mean suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichikawa Setsuko threw herself off that bridge to her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I might kill the Ghost Cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Oh no! I have to get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I never did believe that she committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one who testified she was having trouble at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and she really was having trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had a good lead, but couldn’t follow it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No use writing an article with too little information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I had to—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure she didn’t just give up on it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she was determined to rise to the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was just a newbie reporter, and\Na woman to boot, but she had skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her future was incredibly bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, is there anyone here who saw it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there isn’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A witness, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, the case was closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn’t be any problem with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this girl here saw Ichikawa Setsuko looking depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it you said, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weaker the dog, the louder its bark, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh—What I said then, was…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn’t be that it wasn’t a suicide, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It had to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you remembered her name, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichikawa Setsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W—Well, she was in the newspaper, so of course, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I—I was just talking to myself, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she’s dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B—Because I don’t remember too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know anything! I saw nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the detective told me something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Told you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That there was someone who saw\NSetsuko-san walking near the Kirigahara Bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that was why they were investigating it as a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he just said there were no witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I thought it was odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don’t understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her shoes were neatly arranged on top of the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn’t someone have faked her suicide, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said there was a witness when you came to question me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ask them leading questions, Kadowaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I {\i1}did{\i0} try to lead them in one direction or\Nanother, nobody said anything to contradict me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsuko-san’s death
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was a faked
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!{\alpha&HFF&} Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!{\alpha&HFF&} Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! Stop!{\alpha&HFF&} Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!{\alpha&HFF&} Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!{\alpha&HFF&} Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!{\alpha&HFF&} Stop! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!{\alpha&HFF&} Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!{\alpha&HFF&} Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S—S—Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S—S—Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were we
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rescued?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn’t look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open this door immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I—I—I didn’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t care!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you lot, I’ve got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn’t it opening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can finally go back, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200}A trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t care, as long as we can get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M—Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:11:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this is the Ghost Cat’s doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you leave, your lives will be forfeited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us, Mr. Medicine Seller!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem content to pass comment,\Nwithout actually helping the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are dead! We have to get out of here, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you get out or not is entirely up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not the one who won the raffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, then? I just got on in his place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did,{\alpha&HFF&} in fact, win?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did, in fact, win?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d like you all to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we assemble all your stories, it will likely form the Regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh, I—I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept quiet, thinking it wasn’t my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in a hurry and didn’t think to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they said it was a suicide in\Nthe newspaper, I figured that was that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot all about it soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man or woman? Which was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn’t a suicide, was it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masao-kun, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It itches! It itches!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes hurt! They hurt, but it itches!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told us…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told us the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it have to take Masao-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell should we know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you’re all hiding something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The medicine seller’s the only sane one among you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichikawa was killed by the mayor’s attaché.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s my suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the truth at last, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don’t have any credible evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I didn’t want to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was the mayor involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people had a vested\Ninterest in this subway’s construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, from the government\Nto the construction companies,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were tapping into a veritable river of cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were the allegations that Ichikawa made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a huge scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to let everyone know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll let you publish it, if you track down one more lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t just let it rot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who we’re up against. We must be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, the night before she died,\NIchikawa told me she had incontrovertible evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I said I was too busy, and turned her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I’d listened then, she might still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:14:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why I came today, abandoning my desk job,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was to trace everything back to\Nthe mayor, and avenge her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the mayor must have killed Setsuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m shocked the mayor would do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a pretty common thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It itches! It itches! Ah, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three more left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need all of you to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I’m just going to die, there’s no use telling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, she’s the one who lied in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always seemed suspicious to me!\NYou’re too ignorant of what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn’t see anything at all, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How{\alpha&HFF&} did you come across this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you{\alpha&HFF&} come across this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you come across this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoshita-san’s the worst of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s the one who ran her over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I didn’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a cat—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You knew it was a living thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’re too many cats to stop! I just thought I hit a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn’t even think to check?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stopped for every cat on the\Ntracks, we’d never keep our schedules!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it {\i1}was{\i0} a cat, does life really mean so little to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat’s life isn’t worth messing\Nup so many peoples’{sp?} schedules for!{three liner}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:29.28,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You’re awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what about you? You’re\Nthe one who said it was a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you know this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I think I’ve seen her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you lied about her being a regular customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the detective is investigating something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Maybe I can get into a newspaper, or even a magazine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to use the situation for your own personal gain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I want to be an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be in the papers and stuff to get famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have a face for the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai Shoujiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However did you get a hold
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In his place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn’t come, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see your wrinkles, you old harlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even your dead husband wouldn’t want you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m no harlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:22.47,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah, that’s what I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.56,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then, what the hell were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.91,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You were out all night! Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:30.54,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shut up! I don’t need to listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:31.44,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that could have been extremely useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only you’d told the truth, it\Nwouldn’t have been called a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Setsuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s rich, coming from your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was close enough to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be arrested for perjury!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn’t say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your crime was the worst of all. I’m sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mayor’s the only criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mr. Medicine Seller?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were listening well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother-in-law didn’t even know I was out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You chose your own happiness over truthful testimony?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s just wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to hear it from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put yourself in my shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to leave while my\Nmother-in-law was asleep and be back by dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to be very careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying I should have just stayed\Ncelibate after my damned husband died?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should have!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right. I saw you eyeing the\Nmedicine seller not minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat fights are so ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, oh man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, oh man, oh man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:58.96,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all thanks to you not stopping your damn train!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:02.32,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,619,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}This is all thanks to you not stopping your damn train!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just doing my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t stop because I thought it was a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you did hit Setsuko-san, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s{\alpha&HFF&} still more?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s still more?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don’t we
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,put an end
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to this?
